{"lemma":"فِسْقٌ","slug":"فِسْقٌ","root":"ف.س.ق","root_slug":"ف-س-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-س-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"فِسْق","root":"فسق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33867"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%90%D8%B3%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to deviate from the commandments of God","examples":[{"text":"فَسَجَدُوا إِلَّا إِبْلِيسَ كَانَ مِنَ الْجِنِّ فَفَسَقَ عَنْ أَمْرِ رَبِّهِ","english":"(please add an English translation of this quotation)"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to come out of the shell (of a ripe date)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of فَسَقَ (fasaqa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of فَسُقَ (fasuqa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33867","headword_ar":"فِسْقٌ","root":"fsq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is an inf. n., (S, O, K,) or a simple subst., (Msb,) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasaqa","text_ar":"فَسَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v]: (S, O, Msb, K:) unless as signifying [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A going forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a departure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is said to be a word unknown before ElIslám, and to have become so much used in its legal acceptation as to be, when so used, conventionally regarded as proper (MF, TA:) [thus used,] it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a going forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"departure, from the right way,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) which is said to be the primary meaning, (TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the way of truth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the truth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which is right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA_in~ahu lafisoqN","text_ar":"وَاـِنَّهُ لَفِسْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K, [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafasiqN","text_ar":"لَفَسِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a strange mistake,]) in the Kur [vi. 121]; (O;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a relinquishment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"neglect, of the command of God;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an inclining to disobedience;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O;) or also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disobedience"},{"kind":"text","text":"[itself]; (K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fujuwrN","text_ar":"فُجُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning as above; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"transgression;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unrighteous, sinful, wicked, vitious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"immoral, conduct"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O, K:) it is said by El-Isbahánee to be a more general term than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuforN","text_ar":"كُفْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; applying to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"few sins, misdeeds, transgressions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acts of disobedience,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also, to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"many,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but is commonly known as applying to the latter: and it is related on the authority of Málik that in the Kur vi. 146 it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is slaughtered:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [being used as a subst.,] it sometimes has a pl., which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusuwqN","text_ar":"فُسُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","Msb","MF","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}